name: Magic M
description:
For the past few years I have been creating Augmented Reality artworks with Eyejack, experimenting with my style, animation and real world interactions. This is one of my earlier AR pieces featuring a girl and her little book of magic. 

Artist: Alexander Hare (Pixelpuncha). 
MP4: 960x960 pixels

High res prints and AR activations are available on request from Pixelpuncha.
